quote.summary: Shanghai Longcheer Technology Co Ltd is a China-based company mainly engaged in the research and development, design, production and manufacturing of intelligent products. The Company mainly provides comprehensive intelligent product services to global consumer electronics brands and technology companies, including original design manufacturer (ODM) services and professional services. The Company offers comprehensive product development and manufacturing services, covering everything from design and simulation to software development, testing, supply chain management, production, and delivery. The Company's main products include smartphones, tablets, as well as artificial intelligence Internet of Things (AIoT) products. The Company mainly conducts its businesses in domestic and overseas markets.
